<span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black">&#8220;I&#8217;m tired of him having unnamed sources,&#8221; Romano said in a Friday interview. &#8220;I question his motivations. Neil Vigdor is not treating us fairly. I just want to be treated fairly. I&#8217;m not being treated
